<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.9.9">
<l>karumāmuki luruvākaṉa luruvāpuṉa luruvā</l>
<l>perumālvarai yuruvāpiṟa vuruvāniṉa turuvā</l>
<l>tirumāmakaḷ maruvuñciṟu puliyūrccala cayaṉat</l>
<l>tarumākaṭa lamutēyuṉa taṭiyēcara ṇāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[You] the form of a large, dark cloud, [you] the form of fire,</l>
<l rend="indent">[you] the form of water,</l>
<l>[You] the form of a huge dark mountain, you the form of [all] other [things],</l>
<l rend="indent">[you] of your [own] form,</l>
<l>Rare great ocean of ambrosia on a watery bed in Ciṟupuliyūr</l>
<l>Where the great lady Tiru embraces [you], only your feet are [my] refuge.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
